{"tid":739458,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯關注禮貌問題 促政府加強德育教育","createTime":"2018-07-12T06:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T12:38:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a65720aebaa816f1491402a6c0270cb4b4818333","tid":739458,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:23:08.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥說，她的教育理念是全人教育，透過教育培養下一代成為德、智、體、群、美兼備的學生，是當局教育工作目標，但成功與否要其他方面配合，包括家長。<br />\n<br />\n議員何君堯在立法會行政長官答問會上說，會前見到民主黨涂謹申與保安理論，質疑為何應讓特首先行通道，何君堯認為，紳士應讓淑女先行，關注禮貌問題，促請政府責成教育局加強德育教育。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥回應說，非常尊重議會內的規則，她無意介入，她與官員都會以禮相待。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%A6%AE%E8%B2%8C%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-%E4%BF%83%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E5%BE%B7%E8%82%B2%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2-050126807.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E8%25B2%258C%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E8%2582%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2-050126807.html&d=b%2BL7yZQHkTtw9lNrjqR4fzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=0bdee26a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%A6%AE%E8%B2%8C%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-%E4%BF%83%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E5%BE%B7%E8%82%B2%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2-050126807.html</a>"},{"pid":"07622b99d737a84ac4295d83878ff7785917d189","tid":739458,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20160513/b7ce003a5fae444d968f6ef63f6a7e16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.mp.itc.cn%2Fupload%2F20160513%2Fb7ce003a5fae444d968f6ef63f6a7e16.jpg&h=27dc831f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ee59dfc2cfebcd3a780cac83993f0535e008990","tid":739458,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"